                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.822/73: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-11-24T12:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 24, 1919, noon.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 173, November 19, 11 a.m.</p>
                <p>Department approves your interpretation of instructions contained in Department’s
                    October 16, 2 p.m., and believes that no further message in connection with
                    Roncador Cay should now be sent. Please inform Department at once if Colombian
                    Government re-initiates the matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
